commitResults.messageBody: Include use case, add an internship application
Include feature(list) and qna.

Update the link of the GitHub Actions build status badge, acknowledge
the original source of the code, update all contents to match our
own project.

* Create new fields for Application

Four fields are created for now which are CompanyName, ContactNumber,
Email and Position Applied.

* Create Application class containing its relevant fields and methods

* Add Predicate classes for keywords search

To be used in FindCommand to assist in keywords search in fields
CompanyName and PositionApplied.

* Add exceptions for Application class

Throw when Application does not exist and duplicated Application is
found

* Create UniqueApplicationList

A list of applications that enforces uniqueness between its elements
and does not allow nulls.

* Rename fields to be shorter

Change PositionApplied to Position, CompanyName to Company,
ContactNumber to Contact. Remove Tags in Application class

* Add Date field for Application and its test

Store value of Date in the form of LocalDate

* Fix trailing whitespace

* Fix checkstyle error

* Fix checkstyle error for test

* Add Date field into Application class

* Create new fields for Interview class

Interview is a field for Application

* Fix Company javadoc

Standardize dateString input format so that isValidDate() can be used
for the return type of toString() method of LocalDate type instance.

LocalDate toString() return type: String in yyyy-MM-dd format.
Date isValidDate() take in parameter with same format as above.
